OL,3,CDressage competitors grow concerned
OL,4,Cover the sport's future
OL,6,FMaxime explains: "It is a massive
OL,7,Fconcern because, without the core
OL,8,Fcommittee, the competitions cannot be
OL,9,Fput on.
OL,11,F"It is a massive worry for us at the
OL,12,Fmoment."
OL,14,FTerry Lihou from Guernsey Dressage
OL,15,Fsays that they need the younger
OL,16,Fgeneration to take more interest in
OL,17,Fsecuring dressage's survival on the
OL,18,Fisland.
