OL,3,CDressage competitors grow concerned
OL,4,Cover the sport's future
OL,6,FHe explains: "Guernsey as a whole we
OL,7,Fare low on active young riders who are
OL,8,Fcompeting. Our junior section is quite
OL,9,Flow."
OL,11,FThe Bailiwick has had some recent good
OL,12,Fpress following Sark's Carl Hester
OL,13,Fwinning his fourth Olympic medal in
OL,14,Fdressage this year.
OL,16,FHowever, Terry believes video footage
OL,17,Fof Charlotte Dujardin that showed her
OL,18,Frepeatedly whipping a horse in
OL,19,Ftraining earlier this year has not
OL,20,Fhelped dressage's reputation.
