OL,4,Cover the sport's future
OL,6,FTerry says: "The video went viral and
OL,7,Fsince there have been other videos
OL,8,Ffrom other riders worldwide.
OL,10,F"I do think that now the sport of
OL,11,Fequestrianism is under the microscope.
OL,12,FPeople are very very nervous."
OL,14,FDressage judge Alex Harrison-West also
OL,15,Fbelieves there are barriers in terms
OL,16,Fof financial support.
OL,18,FHe says: "You are probably looking at
OL,19,F(spending), easily, #500 a month
OL,20,Fminimum.
